hopobject.body: What's the exchange rate for euros? eva cebrian prisa radio The stock market would eventually feel this pain mostacutely. One way of hedging against that is the all-purpose bearETF, the Direxion Daily Total Market Bear 1X ETF. Ittracks the reverse performance of the MSCI U.S. Broad MarketIndex, and charges 0.67 percent of assets annually. Since U.S.stocks as measured by the S&P 500 Index are having a good year -up 16 percent through Oct. 4 - the bear fund is down nearly 19percent through Oct. 4.
